    <item>
      <title>博茨瓦纳的多元化发展有望吸引富裕的非洲人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/botswana-s-diversification-drive-seen-luring-wealthy-africans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究发现，博茨瓦纳正努力实现经济多元化，从采矿业转向金融服务业，这将使其能够与毛里求斯竞争成为非洲高净值个人和家庭的中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/botswana-s-diversification-drive-seen-luring-wealthy-africans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:22:07 GMT</pubDate>
